videos.description: Florida State's Ike Obiagu makes the huge rejection on Clemson's Marcquise Reed's layup attempt.
videos.headline: Ike Obiagu makes the big block

videos.description: As Clemson's Gabe DeVoe drives to the basket, he misses the attempt, but the ball gets stuck between the rim and the backboard.
videos.headline: Gabe DeVoe wedges the ball on the rim

videos.description: Clemson's Clyde Trapp has his 3-pointer bounce off the top of the backboard and off the rim before going into the basket.
videos.headline: Trapp gets the extremely friendly bounce

videos.description: Clemson's Marcquise Reed looks to challenge Kelly Bryant for starting quarterback with a perfect outlet pass to Elijah Thomas, who finishes with a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Thomas makes the football catch and finishes with a dunk
